    <h1>Top 1% Coding Agent<br>Productivity Playbook</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Context engineering, the dumb zone, and 10 actionable tips<br>from the builders who ship fastest</p>
    <p class="meta">From YC's Light Cone ‚Äî Calvin French-Owen (Segment, ex-OpenAI Codex) √ó Gary Tan<br><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qwmmWzPnhog" target="_blank">Watch the full episode ‚Üí</a></p>
